snippet.textDisplay: Many of you are asking about why Rituraj was banned to sing this song afterwards. It's because of "bande Utkal janani". It's the state anthem of Odisha. And since it was mixed with a folk song, it's kinda disrespect towards the anthem. It's just like we mix our national anthem "Jana Gana Mana" with a Punjabi hit song where everyone is jumping and all, where's as when national anthem/ state anthem is played one must stand in attention as a token of respect towards the state/nation. Hence this is the reason why it was not taken lightly.

और सोना तो खरा सोना है,क्या कहने आपके मैम।
